8
[p 
	"After the releases of DQMJ series, the original DQM is being forgotten. DQM2 seems to be the most forgotten title in DQM series. But, I love it and had played it for 100 hours in childhood. so I decided to make a decent TAS.  
	$LF
]p
[pre 
	$LF
]pre
