[p 
	"Testrun(no bug, no detailed investigation before making): http://www.nicovideo.jp/watch/sm17186038
	$LF
]p
[p 
	"This game has 2 useful glitches for TAS.
	$LF
]p
[ul 
	[li 
		" Cloakroom bug (預かり所バグ); It's fixed in USA version. That's why I chose JPN version.
		$LF
	]li
]ul
[p 
	"Where a person is next to a door or a well or a stair, we press A repeatedly in entering. The conversation will start before the map loading. The map ID will change to the next map, but the map itself is same as previous map.
	$LF
	"So, we can go where we can't go originally.
	$LF
]p
[ul 
	[li 
		" Scrolling bug
		$LF
	]li
]ul
[p 
	"Before when we go down and the screen is scrolling, press up and down.
	$LF
	"then the character's location will slide out the half of the grid and we can go where we can't go originally.
	$LF
]p
[h3 
	" Stage by stage comments
	$LF
]h3
[p 
	"I'm not going to mention the full story(too much to write all), but only the shortcuts and notable things.
	$LF
	"The glitches are often used to save walking time.
	$LF
	"in some world, they are also used to cut the scenario.
	$LF
]p
[h4 
	" From start to entering the first world
	$LF
]h4
[p 
	"Nothing. The glitches are used and they save some seconds of the boringsome walking time. 
	$LF
]p
[h4 
	" The first world (Desert World, さばくのせかい)
	$LF
]h4
[p 
	"Using Cloakroom bug into well, it's possible to call the mid-boss.
	$LF
	"2 events are cut. About 2 minutes are saved from Testrun.
	$LF
]p
[h4 
	" The second world (Sea World, みずのせかい)
	$LF
]h4
[p 
	"We can logically skip all scenario in this world, but then we can't proceed the scenario in the next world.
	$LF
	"I skipped scenario as possible and take MoonRock（つきのいし） as an additional treasure. ;D
	$LF
	"CallHelp(なかまをよぶ, {Lv(-1?)}*2*4 damage in TAS) is very useful there and it actually saved much time.
	$LF
]p
[p 
	"With reducing waste frames to manipulate, I gathered money to buy items in the next world.
	$LF
]p
[h4 
	" The third world (Ice World, こおりのせかい)
	$LF
]h4
[p 
	"Bought items at the shop in Norden（ノールデン）.
	$LF
	"We can't choose another shop, because it's the only shop that sells LogTwig before using.
	$LF
	"All the event and mid-boss in Norden, Nofor, Goldmines are skipped by the scrolling glitch.
	$LF
	"The rest are "normal", just walking ridiculous routes to shorten time.
	$LF
]p
[h4 
	" The fourth world (Sky World, てんくうのせかい) and The Last World
	$LF
]h4
[p 
	"Skipping half of the scenarios by scrolling bug and just collect the 3 items which are needed to battle the boss.
	$LF
	"BigTrip （かんけつせん, damages 0~15% of enemy's MAX HP）saves much time in 3 bosses - NiteRich（ナイトリッチ, HP1500）, Mudou (ムドー, HP3000), Darck(ドーク, HP4000).
	$LF
]p
[h4 
	" Ending
	$LF
]h4
[p 
	"hmm, it has some dialogue after Ending credits to see "The END". it makes final input 7 mins longer.
	$LF
]p
